  "code": "stateDiagram-v2\n    [Education_LMS_Portal] --> New : Process created\n    New --> Ready : Admit (Education_StudentDB)\n    Ready --> Running : Dispatch (Education_GradeSync)\n    Running --> Waiting : I/O or event wait\n    Running --> Ready : Interrupt (Education_ClassroomService)\n    Running --> Terminated : Exit (Education_LMS_Portal)\n    \n    Waiting --> Ready : I/O completed\n    Waiting --> Suspended_Wait : Swap out (Education_ContentCDN)\n    Suspended_Wait --> Suspended_Ready : I/O completed\n    Suspended_Ready --> Ready : Swap in (Education_ContentCDN)\n    \n    Terminated --> [Education_ClassroomService]",
