      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育平台设计一个进程状态流转图，核心是LMS门户的进程生命周期管理。起点应该是Education_LMS_Portal，进程创建后进入New状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "New"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，起点是LMS门户。那从New状态到Ready的转换条件是什么？需要涉及哪些教育子系统？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "New",
        "Ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Admit操作，由Education_StudentDB负责学生数据验证后准入。然后Ready状态通过Dispatch进入Running，这里需要Education_GradeSync来调度成绩相关的计算任务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "New",
        "Ready",
        "Running",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Admit",
        "Dispatch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经添加了从New到Ready的Admit转换，标注Education_StudentDB，以及Ready到Running的Dispatch转换，标注Education_GradeSync。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "New",
        "Ready",
        "Running",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Running状态需要能回到Ready，当Education_ClassroomService发出Interrupt时，比如课堂服务需要抢占资源。另外Running还要能到Waiting，这是普通的I/O等待。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
        "Ready",
        "Waiting",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Interrupt"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Running到Ready是Interrupt触发，涉及ClassroomService；Running到Waiting是I/O或事件等待，这个不需要标注具体服务对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
        "Ready",
        "Waiting",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，I/O等待是通用行为。但Running终止时要回到Education_LMS_Portal，通过Exit操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Terminated",
        "Exit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Running到Terminated的Exit转换，标注Education_LMS_Portal。现在Waiting状态的处理呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
        "Terminated",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Waiting有两个去向：I/O完成后回到Ready；或者被Swap out到Suspended_Wait，这涉及Education_ContentCDN的内容分发网络，当内存紧张时把等待进程换出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Waiting",
        "Ready",
        "Suspended_Wait",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Swap"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。Waiting到Ready标注I/O completed，Waiting到Suspended_Wait标注Swap out和Education_ContentCDN。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Waiting",
